{"tid":951284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"20年來最暖冬至　中午高見25度　元旦日或低至12度","createTime":"2018-12-22T08:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T08:24:50.000Z","uid":138557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9005ef8634bfe342e14943b0c663f59b40aa89","tid":951284,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:12:51.000Z","msg":"今日冬至，天文台下午1時錄得約25度，是繼1998年冬至錄得最高氣溫25.7度後，氣溫最高的一次。<br />\n<br />\n天文台指，一股溫暖的偏東氣流正影響廣東沿岸；今日下午部分時間有陽光，天氣溫暖，吹和緩東至東北風。<br />\n<br />\n下周後期氣溫顯著下降。據天文台預測，下周五（28日）最低氣溫15度，周日（30日）氣溫最低跌至13度，元旦日（明年1月1日）有機會低見12度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u200bFy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu200bFy.gif&h=c243e9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20181222/s00001/1545456299535/20%e5%b9%b4%e4%be%86%e6%9c%80%e6%9a%96%e5%86%ac%e8%87%b3-%e4%b8%ad%e5%8d%88%e9%ab%98%e8%a6%8b25%e5%ba%a6-%e5%85%83%e6%97%a6%e6%97%a5%e6%88%96%e4%bd%8e%e8%87%b312%e5%ba%a6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20181222%2Fs00001%2F1545456299535%2F20%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%259c%2580%25e6%259a%2596%25e5%2586%25ac%25e8%2587%25b3-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%258d%2588%25e9%25ab%2598%25e8%25a6%258b25%25e5%25ba%25a6-%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%2597%25a6%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%2588%2596%25e4%25bd%258e%25e8%2587%25b312%25e5%25ba%25a6&d=ZH4yc4t%2FNb3Zc6B%2FQrMq5whMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c0f7d3e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20181222%2Fs00001%2F1545456299535%2F20%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e4%25be%2586%25e6%259c%2580%25e6%259a%2596%25e5%2586%25ac%25e8%2587%25b3-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%258d%2588%25e9%25ab%2598%25e8%25a6%258b25%25e5%25ba%25a6-%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%2597%25a6%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%2588%2596%25e4%25bd%258e%25e8%2587%25b312%25e5%25ba%25a6&h=ad2dcca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20181222/s00001/1545456299535/20%e5%b9%b4%e4%be%86%e6%9c%80%e6%9a%96%e5%86%ac%e8%87%b3-%e4%b8%ad%e5%8d%88%e9%ab%98%e8%a6%8b25%e5%ba%a6-%e5%85%83%e6%97%a6%e6%97%a5%e6%88%96%e4%bd%8e%e8%87%b312%e5%ba%a6</a>"},{"pid":"40de276b53da55ec47f07607eba133c84be6634e","tid":951284,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36454e60d33f83ae9c6db4fd601db22c74b2722d","tid":951284,"uid":138557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T08:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}